    Format[edit]

    • Group Stage: 11th - 20th February, 2022
      • Four double-elimination format (GSL) groups
        • Each group has 4 teams
        • All matches are Bo3
      • Top 2 teams from each group advances to Playoffs
    • Playoffs: 23rd - 27th February, 2022
      • 8 teams, Double-elimination bracket
      • All matches (excl. Grand Final) are Bo3
      • Grand Final is Bo5
